Once things are setup, you can press <b>Next</b>.   While you are recording your lecture this screen will still be visible but not moveable, so before you press <b>Next</b>, make sure to move the screen where you want it. 

In general is it <i>not</i> necessary to use the <b>Source</b>, <b>Format</b>, or <b>Compression</b> buttons.  Usually the defaults are just fine.
